This book is for all those readers of the original Homemade C-4 who wrote to ask for alternatives that eliminated the need for costly, hard-to-find ingredients, especially nitromethane. These recipes are dirt-simple; feature widely found, inexpensive, unregulated chemicals and can be assembled in no time
